Usage: loadIoFile [-help] <file_name> [-noAdjustDieSize] [-specifiedIosOnly] [-ECO  [-padsOnly  | -bumpsOnly ]]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<file_name>                # file to be loaded (string, required)
-ECO                       # use IO file to perform IO/Bump ECO
                           # (bool, optional)
-bumpsOnly                 # only do bump ECO operation (bool, optional)
-noAdjustDieSize           # don't adjust die size (bool, optional)
-padsOnly                  # only do pad ECO operation (bool, optional)
-specifiedIosOnly          # only load the io in the specified io file
                           # (bool, optional)